{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3bd7774e4d","title":"汪东兴在中央工作会议上的一次讲话摘要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6dc2c9bbb3","index":0,"year":1977,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"3bd7774e4d"}],"tags":[{"id":"3c11982f62","name":"汪东兴","type":"人物"},{"id":"b88b47c25d","name":"批邓反击右倾翻案风","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"fb776baaf9","name":"邓小平","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"e7b164baf1","name":"汪东兴"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d742796884","type":"title","text":"汪东兴在中央工作会议上的一次讲话摘要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3bd7774e4d"},{"id":"7af639c5cc","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，有人提出“批邓、反击右倾翻案风”搞错了，要把邓小平请出来，还要让他当总理，说他如何如何能干。邓小平这个人我是熟悉的，讲能力他是有一点，但错误更多。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3bd7774e4d"},{"id":"8bf5e2fbf2","type":"paragraph","text":"1975年，毛主席是想让他当总理，可试了试，不行，他那两下子比我们华主席差远了，所以，最后毛主席才选定华国锋同志作接班人……","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3bd7774e4d"}],"page":{"id":"8668d04c0f","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3bd7774e4d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}